{"tid":1434701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"運動dress code 係時間要轉七彩色","createTime":"2019-08-09T00:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:02:11.000Z","uid":296083,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e84890f8143d5201f04a917dc73e68e7d38fe27","tid":1434701,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:35:14.000Z","msg":"純討論 大家會唔會考慮改變運動dress code穿不同顏色 （除左藍白）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實只要我地係一心5大訴求 必然會見到大家</span></span></span> 轉色有以下幾個好處<br />\n<br />\n1. 轉移視線 - 做回普通街坊 一來避免不必要衝突 林鄭每日記者會目的就係分化 就係想示威者同市民 鞏固支持政府力量 發生衝突只會令中立遊離更抗拒運動 <br />\n<br />\n2.方便前線勇武徹退 - 黑警難以憑衣服辦認<br />\n<br />\n3. 改變形象 - 黑色給予人恐怖分子黑社會感覺 七彩顏色一改形象令運動繼續落去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">純粹意見 不篤灰 不分化 不割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"99ab90c2765f2e04f07a77a0caaa49db173cd6aa","tid":1434701,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:35:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"063a6e1eeb75e801aaaaf2526c0e8df73af76c40","tid":1434701,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:36:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59251690ebd8d1fc0798a7d19eac0cbdfbeb5d78","tid":1434701,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"重可以話比人知我地係無大台"},{"pid":"1c88d6f737968c2e02a54e19c308d5e5877bb6e1","tid":1434701,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:37:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a2b16b68e1eda63edde071d8c1fb6b6801859d7","tid":1434701,"uid":296083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa563fd4d7b5ed42cf1b6d4e7cded885a679c032","tid":1434701,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:37:51.000Z","msg":"你d黑社會真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"0b89f496813c19889f4d7070edaa3341a831c55a","tid":1434701,"uid":134323,"lik